Description: Our Audrey sofa has a curved silhouette that is outlined with a welted border to accent the beautiful shape.   Audrey has a soft shape that allows the frame to float in a room setting.

The Baldwin series is part of our Washable Slipcover Collection featuring a thin cut-a-way arm, high back detail and a flanged trim detail on the seat cushion and back pillow.  Baldwin features a chair, swivel chair and sofa lengths.

Clean lines and alluring depths define this vast seating collection. Bank's trim track arms, loose seat and back cushions are paired with a kidney pillow for added comfort and visual interest.  This vast seating collection consists of: 90" sofa, lounge chair, swivel chair, left/right arm sofa, left/right arm corner sofa, left/right arm loveseat, left/right arm chaise, left/right arm chair, armless loveseat, corner chair, armless chair, swivel chair, ottoman, bumper ottoman and cocktail ottoman.

Punctuated by trim sloping track arms, Beckett's shapely silhouette balances clean lines with ample comfort. Deep inprofile and streamlined for sophistication, Beckett rests on simple block feet and features loose seat and back cushions. Beckett isoffered in 80", 90" and 100" sofas with matching lounge and swivel chair. Made in America.
